2008 ग्रीष्मकालीन ओलंपिक टेनिस

टेनिस competitions at the 2008 ग्रीष्मकालीन ओलंपिक in Beijing will be held from 10 अगस्त to 17 अगस्त. The tournaments will be held at the Olympic Green Tennis Centre. The surface will be hardcourt, specifically DecoTurf.

Surface - DecoTurf II

The tennis competition at the Olympic Games consists of a single elimination tournament. The 2 losers in the semifinal will play for the bronze medal.

Matches will be best-of-3 sets, except for the Men's singles and doubles finals which will be best-of-5 sets. No tiebreak will be played in the final set.

